            "fields": {
              "name": "About Page 2nd Section | Hero 2",
              "heading": "We bridge the gap between vision and execution.",
              "eyebrow": "THE BYTEFLOW APPROACH",
              "subText": "We observed a critical gap in the technology consulting landscape: firms either offered high-level strategic advice with no implementation capability, or provided low-cost development resources that lacked enterprise architectural vision.\n\nByteFlow bridges that gap. We are a deep-tech engineering firm that embeds with our clients to solve their hardest technical challenges. Our teams don't just take orders — we challenge assumptions, design robust architectures, and deliver production code that scales."
            }
